ificantly reduce water consumption compared to conventional methods."}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"p-6 bg-muted rounded-lg","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"font-semibold text-primary mb-4","children":"Waste Reduction"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-sm text-foreground/70","children":"Through circular design practices and responsible production methods, we minimize waste. We encourage customers to care for and maintain their pieces for longevity."}]]}]]}]]}]]}]}]
